description.content:

Special things you get from my services:


=> Unlimited Revisions

NOTE: It's very important to send a message before ordering, I will try to give a response in just 5 minutes!


Thanks, Ali

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: First and most important, I will need to know as much as possible about you and your business, that way I'll be able to make you a site that truly represents you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is SEO optimized website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: SEO or Search Engine Website Is one which is compatible with search engine rules having a SEO friendly Url structure, layout, optimized images etc. Website which i will develop will be fully SEO optimized.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will my website be SEO Optimized?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, your website will be highly SEO optimized.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is the responsive design?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Responsive website design is the approach that suggests that design and development should respond to the user's behavior and environment based on screen size, platform and orientation.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Does my website will be Responsive (Mobile, Desktops, and Tablets Friendly)?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, it will be 100% mobile, tablets and desktop friendly. Responsive website is the modern trend in website development it means that the website will be fully compatible to all mobile devices and adjust itself according to the screen size.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I be able to easily modify the contents of the site?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Absolutely! Once the website is done, you will be able to not only change the texts and images with a few clicks, but also to change the whole layout or add new pages. You will also be provided with the user manual of the website this will make the things a lot easier.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is a User manual?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: A User manual or Documentation is a document which contains guidelines for making changes/edits or updates in website through admin panel.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if I am not satisfied?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will keep working on your website until you are 100% satisfied. But still if you are not happy with the work I will refund you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Are you available for customized order?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I am available for customized order and I will provide you a custom quote for that.
